        " «لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ وَ هُوَ طَهُورٌ فَلاَ تَتَّقِهِ أَنْ يُصِيبَكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2613 - Sama'ah asked Imam (as) about a man whose garment is stained with the saffron of the Ka'bah while he is in the state of Ihram.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it; it is pure, so do not avoid it if it touches you.\""
        ]
      }
